":"男的也好"},{"pid":"158d568bcb8721a166abcc815ae8887b2bd4da34","tid":2062403,"uid":335283,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"244893b023d5342f8e7fe59a24da4cd0df3d329f","tid":2062403,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T06:36:15.000Z","msg":"男人老狗都無反抗能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n男主管係清水健咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T07:53:48.000Z","msg":"清水健可以搞到個個男人老狗潮吹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9978086548f1192fb58070a1ad2d9b27b4bdf4f7","tid":2062403,"uid":222155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c422a12e60b446004b9098a745c01e48e8d7105","tid":2062403,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T06:05:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/bMjOWo0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FbMjOWo0.jpg&h=d71fbca0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/b0nQFem.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fb0nQFem.png&h=3bbdfaa9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲西岡健吾被指就是遭性侵的男藝人。（圖／翻攝自西岡健吾IG）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1.媒體來源:<br />\nettoday<br />\n<br />\n2.記者署名:<br />\n田暐瑋<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3.完整新聞標題:<br />\n被男主管「拖進廁所性侵30分鐘」！ 22歲男偶像慘當性奴<br />\n<br />\n4.完整新聞內文:<br />\n<br />\n日本知名娛樂公司「渡邊娛樂」日前驚爆男高層對旗下男藝人長期性侵的醜聞，男藝人礙<br />\n於對方地位不敢反抗，遭高層帶回家性侵，還趁熟睡時偷拍裸照，高層甚至傳了許多猥褻<br />\n訊息，讓受害人不堪其擾。有網友根據報導提供的相關線索，猜出受害藝人的真實身份，<br />\n應該就是外型秀氣的22歲男星西岡健吾。<br />\n<br />\n《週刊文春》踢爆渡邊娛樂醜聞，內容指出47歲的常務大澤剛從2018年底開始至2019年，<br />\n趁著受害藝人找他商量退團一事時進行性侵害，多次要求受害者當自己女友，兩人一起搭<br />\n計程車趕通告時，他還把手強硬伸進對方褲子裡撫摸，之後還帶受害者進工作場合的廁所<br />\n性侵，不只口交，還進行手指性侵，全程20至30分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有網友根據線索猜測，遭到狼爪侵犯的藝人應該就是渡邊娛樂旗下的Mag!c Prince前成員<br />\n－西岡健吾，年僅22歲，外型秀氣陰柔，臉蛋精緻，若是扮成女孩也毫無違和。渡邊娛樂<br />\n是日本知名娛樂公司，大胃王曾根辣妹、AKB48的柏木由紀也都是該公司藝人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n5.完整新聞連結 (或短網址):<br />\n<a href=\"https://star.ettoday.net/news/1736848?redirect=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstar.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F1736848%3Fredirect%3D1&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJroeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=6fa11b95\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://star.ettoday.net/news/1736848?redirect=1</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T08:16:58.000Z","msg":"定延好危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8af1ff2e5a25456a92379da301cd3ce270ca447a","tid":2062403,"uid":41366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T08:23:45.000Z","msg":"拎去氣炸未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}